product: SPIDERCASE [3 IN 1] Designed for iPhone 13 Pro Max Case, [Crystal Clear Not Yellowing][with 2 Pcs Tempered Glass Screen Protectors & 2 Pcs Camera Lens Protectors] Slim Thin Case-Clear
title: Love this case!
body: I really like this case...better than I thought I would. I ordered the clear glitter and my husband got the plain clear.  He said he wishes he got the glitter because it makes the back of the phone look really cool.  Each case came with 2 screen protectors and 2 sets of camera protectors (which are also glitter and very glam). My husband said that the screen protectors are blue light blockers too, I didn't even realize that when I bought them.  I have always been hesitant to purchase a plastic case, but this case is different.  It feels rubbery around the edges. We have Iphone 13 pro max and the cases fit perfectly! For those of you who think it doesn't fit, you got to put a little effort into it, it is supposed to be snug.  I highly recommend these cases!!

product: SPIDERCASE [3 IN 1] Designed for iPhone 13 Pro Max Case, [Crystal Clear Not Yellowing][with 2 Pcs Tempered Glass Screen Protectors & 2 Pcs Camera Lens Protectors] Slim Thin Case-Clear
body: I was truly happy with my purchase. The case is great, you get a 2 screen protectors and you get a 2 small protectors for your camera. The case fits perfectly and the screen protector has worked great. My only complaint is that I’ve had this for about 2 weeks and the case for my camera has broken. I haven’t dropped my phone. It hasn’t been hit on anything and I was surprised to see that my camera case was broken. So now I’m using the second camera case and currently searching for a new case.

product: SPIDERCASE [3 IN 1] Designed for iPhone 13 Pro Max Case, [Crystal Clear Not Yellowing][with 2 Pcs Tempered Glass Screen Protectors & 2 Pcs Camera Lens Protectors] Slim Thin Case-Clear
title: Perfect fit
body: This fit my iPhone 13pro max perfectly. The screen protector fit the screen entirely but leaves just the right amount of space for the case to go on and fit snugly on the phone with out interfering with the screen and vise versa. The camera lens protector is a think protector that fits the shape of the camera lens group and does not interfere with the cameras, even when zoomed all the way out for ultra wide angle. A previous phone and previous case gave me that problem. The lens protector, although thick, does not stick out past the case, everything fits very well together.No info on longevity or durability yet, but I have confidence this will work well for me.

title: Great case but…
body: The case is great, seems durable, helps provide a good grip on the phone, nice and clear, the one that I chose was clear screen protector is nice, it went on easily  My only complaint is the cameras protector. The protector has a mild adhesive on it to help stick to the phone, but as soon as you put it on the sticky stuff gets distorted in the area over the LiDAR sensor, that distortion then causes the camera to not focus properly. So besides this camera protector issue this is a great buy. Even without the camera protectors it’s still a good purchase.

title: Quality is higher than the price tag might suggest
body: Quality is almost shocking and the thoughtfulness that went into the design and implementation is appreciated. The case is well made and the buttons press properly like on more expensive alternatives. The camera protector square and the 2 screen protectors fit perfectly. If you put the case on first, the screen protector and camera protector will glide themselves into place perfectly. It’s satisfying to put together because for once the entire product and accessories makes sense and was well thought out. It’s insane that this quality is rare, but this is the one to buy. Very happy with my purchase.
